Ligation-fidelity matrices (seqforge-fidelity)
----------------------------------------------

Overhang ligation-frequency counts in
`crates/seqforge-fidelity/src/fidelity_generated.rs` are unaltered published
supplementary data redistributed under Creative Commons
Attribution-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (CC BY-ND 4.0), packaged via
Edinburgh Genome Foundry tatapov_data
(https://github.com/Edinburgh-Genome-Foundry/tatapov_data).

Sources include Potapov et al., ACS Synth. Biol. 7(11):2665–2674 (2018)
(doi: 10.1021/acssynbio.8b00333) and Pryor et al., PLoS ONE 15(9):e0238592
(2020) (doi: 10.1371/journal.pone.0238592). Scoring code is original SeqForge
(MIT). See `crates/seqforge-fidelity/ATTRIBUTION.md` for full citations and
license notes.

